<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>FORFEO LAB | Excellence Client Québec</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .nav-link { font-weight: 600; color: #333; }
        .stat-card { border: none; border-radius: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; }
        .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0d6efd; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white border-bottom p-3">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">FORFEO <span class="text-primary">LAB</span></a>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/audit-mystere">Audit Mystère</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/forfaits">Forfaits</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/ambassadeurs">Devenir Ambassadeur</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link btn btn-primary text-white rounded-pill px-4 ms-lg-3" href="/login">Connexion</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container my-5 py-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">Pourquoi mesurer votre impact au Québec ?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">Les entreprises qui ne sondent pas leur clientèle perdent du terrain.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">82%</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold mt-2">Des Québécois changent d'enseigne après une seule mauvaise expérience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">1/26</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold mt-2">Seul 1 client mécontent sur 26 se plaint, les autres partent sans rien dire.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">+15%</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold mt-2">Augmentation moyenne du CA pour les entreprises utilisant l'audit mystère.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">FORFEO en action</h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="ratio ratio-16x9 bg-dark rounded-4 shadow overflow-hidden"><video src="" controls></video></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="ratio ratio-16x9 bg-dark rounded-4 shadow overflow-hidden"><video src="" controls></video></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="ratio ratio-16x9 bg-dark rounded-4 shadow overflow-hidden"><video src="" controls></video></div></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="forfy-btn" style="position:fixed; bottom:25px; right:25px; cursor:pointer; z-index:1000;">
        <img src="/ForfyLogo.png" style="width:65px;">
    </div>
    <div id="forfy-chat" style="display:none; position:fixed; bottom:100px; right:25px; width:320px; background:white; border-radius:20px; box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border:1px solid #eee; overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="background:#0d6efd; color:white; padding:15px; font-weight:bold;">Forfy - Assistant FORFEO</div>
        <div id="forfy-msgs" style="height:300px; padding:15px; overflow-y:auto; font-size:0.9rem;"></div>
        <div style="padding:10px; border-top:1px solid #eee;"><input type="text" id="forfy-input" class="form-control rounded-pill" placeholder="Posez une question..."></div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/forfy-brain.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
